host_about:
I am a Stockholmer, born and raised; brought up at Södermalm but recently moved to Fruängen, a suburb in Stockholm with a local centre/market place and lots of greenery, yet close to the "big city". 

I want to provide a more cozy option than hotels and by that encourage you to visit the city and country of mine - one day I might swing by yours :) You are very much welcome to stay in my home and if you need any help while staying here, no problem asking and I will do my best. 

//Elin
